Cloud-Native Pattern Introdcution:

- As we wrap up our exploration of the fundamental concepts of web API development using ASP.NET Core,
    it is time to embark on a journey to explore more advanced topics. In this chapter, we will transition
    from the basics to delve into topics that are important for developers aspiring to master web API
    development. 
- We will delve into the following topics in this chapter:
    • Domain-driven design
    • Clean architecture
    • Microservices
    • Web API design patterns